  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Bash the <strong>lemongrass</strong> with a <strong>rolling</strong> <strong>pin</strong>, remove the <strong>tough</strong> <strong>outer</strong> <strong>layers</strong> and chop the <strong>softer</strong> <strong>inner</strong> <strong>core<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into 4 <span class=\"text-danger\">[8]</span></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Slice 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>red</strong> <strong>chilli</strong> into rounds and finely chop the remaining</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
