    {
      "instruction": "<p>Zest the <strong>lime<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> (try to grate lightly with a micro-plane or sharp box grater and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter)</p><p>Roll the <strong>lime<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice) and cut in half</p><p>Combine the<strong> Chinese rice wine</strong> and <strong>soy</strong> <strong>sauce </strong>in a small bowl with the <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>sesame</strong> <strong>oil</strong>, the juice of the <strong>lime<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> and a splash of <strong>cold water</strong> – this is your <strong>marinade</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
