      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>aromatic basa en papillote </strong>with<strong> </strong>the <strong>ginger & carrot rice </strong>and <strong>caramelised</strong> <strong>onion</strong> <strong>spinach </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle over any <strong>remaining sauce </strong>from the parcels and garnish with the <strong>reserved</strong> <strong>chilli</strong> <strong>rounds</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
